            "title": "退役汽車電池處置壓力漸增 中國出台新規強化管理",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"退役汽車電池處置壓力漸增 中國出台新規強化管理\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ero0jW5lQO2LeD1WCBtdrQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-01/a308ace0-e6b1-11f0-9fe1-5cb85266cb36\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">退役汽車電池處置壓力漸增 中國出台新規強化管理</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
