        },
        {
            "title": "日圓觀察人士面臨日本央行、大選不確定性的雙重打擊",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 隨著日本央行下周會議臨近以及日本提前大選的不確定性加劇，日圓交易員擔心該貨幣可能再度波動。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本周早些時候，<a class=\"link yahoo-link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:日圓;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E5%85%8C%E6%8F%9B-%E6%97%A5%E5%85%83-%E6%97%A5%E5%9C%93-jpy-yen-%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C-%E6%89%BE%E6%8F%9B%E5%BA%97-%E5%85%8C%E6%8F%9B%E5%83%B9-%E7%8F%BE%E9%88%94%E5%83%B9-%E9%9B%BB%E5%8C%AF%E5%83%B9-tt-035656405.html\">日圓</a>一度跌至18個月低點，由於市場預期首相高市早苗將舉行大選，此舉或將鞏固其地位並允許增加政府支出。日本財務大臣和最高外匯事務官員也就此發出警告。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「如果不說幾個月，美元-日圓在過去幾周都沒有波動，但隨著這條選舉新聞的發布，美元-日圓突然上漲，」State Street Bank &amp; Trust東京分行經理Bart Wakabayashi表示：「市場波動還將持續。」</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-e2fbfb68-7380-3cf5-b951-93b282bef280-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據自民黨干事長及其執政聯盟夥伴的共同領導人透露，高市早苗已告知執政聯盟官員，她將於1月19日公佈更多關於解散眾議院的細節。投資者也將密切關注日本央行行長植田和男在下周五的政策會議上就央行加息路徑發出的任何信號。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日圓跌幅加深引發對日本可能干預以支撐日圓匯率的擔憂。官員們表示，他們更關注匯率的波動性和走勢速度，而非具體的匯率水平。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/P5CiD2.10ZaAXfmBrQGynA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/7453ded08e1f9f885734478a52717691\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本周，日圓一度跌至159.45，周五上午徘徊在158.65附近。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Mercer Inc.亞洲區多元資產主管Cameron Systermans表示「鑒於160是一個心理關口，市場將密切關注這一水平。」他補充道，鑒於美元兌日圓在2024年觸及161.95的高點時曾引發干預，因此162很可能成為下一個主要關注點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Yen Watchers Face Double Whammy of BOJ, Election Uncertainty</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">—聯合報導 John Cheng.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%97%A5%E5%9C%93%E8%A7%80%E5%AF%9F%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E9%9D%A2%E8%87%A8%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C-%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%B8%E4%B8%8D%E7%A2%BA%E5%AE%9A%E6%80%A7%E7%9A%84%E9%9B%99%E9%87%8D%E6%89%93%E6%93%8A-005011219.html",
